text: Hoodrich Tales is a first extended play by Big Baby Tape. Released on June 1, 2018 by Warner Music Russia, the EP features guest appearances by Tape LaFlare, ALIZÁDE, Boulevard Depo, Polyana, and Feduk. The first single from Hoodrich Tales, "Hustle Tales" featuring Feduk, was released on March 8, 2018. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2018 debut EPs
